      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is in poor condition and is ready for someone with a vision to give it a complete makeover. It\u2019s a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to roll up your sleeves and bring a classic back to its former glory. If you're looking for a rewarding restoration project, this is the one for you!",
