    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior presents very well, showing only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches that are common for its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, it remains strong and reliable, with a complete service history available for review. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car without the 'new' price tag.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
